➜看懂《信条》也没用，反正你脑子是假的
http://www.sohu.com/a/417735842_624188	28661
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200911/b5ad2e2d5d6944c283e02c3c4e0e4e29.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最近</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管有没有看完<strong>《信条》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">童鞋们都被整懵了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脑子都炸了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一度怀疑自己的智商在给世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拖 后 腿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200911/cf17217a4106428b8158334b2d87f977.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能成功整懵一群有小学中学文凭的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是<strong>《时间简史》狂魔</strong>——<strong>诺兰</strong>引入的物理概念：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>时 间 逆 转</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在咱们的<strong>熵增世界</strong>里</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
*熵增世界：熵增是时间流动方向，热水会慢慢变凉，太阳会不断燃烧衰变，直到宇宙的尽头——热寂，我们从过去走向未来。
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">时间是正常往前走的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200911/1c722fe3ce464ac69d6b47200b08dccf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在诺兰的<strong>熵减世界</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
*熵减世界：相反，我们会从未来走向过去。
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">你进入一扇旋转门</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>时间是可以逆转倒流的！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200911/155699aff75349a68f2a76d7bae78a9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以上都不是重点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重点是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能把童鞋们绕晕的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并不是只有时间逆转</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男一男二到底倒带了多少次 ？！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200911/5bfb6c02395a46859aed036e39d6e89a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">电影看不懂不要紧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕想问的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">假如未来时间逆转已经实现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也能逆转了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200911/3e0f908718454296a85d21f39291af0b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当代人长年熬夜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记忆力还<strong>不如老年人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">压根想不起过去发生的事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别说过去了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">10分钟前的事也未必记得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更可怕的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有人灵光一现的记忆是假的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历史上压根没有发生过这件事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200911/4237e7fe696f4fc887a77c048c3bb54f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别怀疑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>记忆诈骗这回事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>是真实存在的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先不讲成人记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据英国<strong>威斯敏斯特大学</strong>研究</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你小时候的记忆都有可能是假的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200911/70de18f587d444758eb49a285af6ecd2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首先</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每次讲到一两岁的丰功伟绩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很多小学鸡都会侃侃而谈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200911/0697c32719444cad90e94c8e1f95067b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">事实是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你至少要到<strong>两岁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大脑这个U盘才会发育出<strong>储存记忆的能力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现实是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你死都想不出这段回忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大部分人会<strong>按照自己想象力</strong>——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>编</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">研究人员称</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大约每10人中就有4个人会编造自己的第一段记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200911/4b2a3bddbbe248eb9a26db4c6210aa5b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算你2岁了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始有记忆了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别高兴太早</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国记忆专家<strong>洛芙迪</strong>表示</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然婴儿能形成记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200911/a5ad107850e14ecfa563ed3c44c6c9f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——那些记忆并不持久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200911/7cbbc11d4f7c4e1eb6952ea55602209f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因此哪怕你到了<strong>七岁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也会出现<strong> “童年记忆缺失症”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">请原谅小孩的童言无忌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了单纯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们的记忆力是真的差啊！！！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200911/28cf97efeb1948f1b04e8982f1f2728c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别说小孩子的记事能力差</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>大人</strong>有时候也会被记忆欺骗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大脑甚至会植入<strong>虚假的记忆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">改写你的历史</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记忆都是假的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕要这聪明的脑子有何用！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200911/69bd33c8af6341ae968517d3facb8f18.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伦敦大学心理学家<strong>Julia Shaw</strong>还证明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让你相信自己实施过<strong>子虚乌有的暴力犯罪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是有可能的！！！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">利用<strong>记忆检索技术</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在三次访谈中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都问参与者关于暴力犯罪的问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200911/6b9810f44f4b44af8f502c16eee20c7f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在适当的环境下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每个人都会形成复杂的虚假记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在有<strong>高度暗示性</strong>的访谈中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你会很容易产生令人不安的虚假记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">关键是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这些回忆都很有细节!</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>感觉悄咪咪被人植入记忆芯片了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200911/77f48fd779144644ab04ac737ce4795a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样看来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>记忆是可以通过心理战术扭曲的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">反派想通过熵减毁灭世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺兰大哥通过时间逆转拯救世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不用那么麻烦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扭曲记忆也同样能搞乱世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是时间<strong>慢一点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200911/d89a73bbf32b4928a602303d991a45ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>最极端的记忆灌输案例</strong>中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">存在着一种有争议的技术：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>回 溯 疗 法</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说白了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是让你<strong>直面案发时的创伤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这些创伤一般隐藏在他们的<strong>潜意识</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200911/28713d4c8041437f93491ea4bebf0c32.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种方式容易诱发<strong>错误的记忆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从而导致错判</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回溯疗法也被心理医生拿来用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">分为<strong>年龄回溯</strong>和<strong>前世回溯</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年龄回溯在国内比较常用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这方法源于精神鼻祖<strong>弗洛伊德</strong>提到的<strong>潜意识</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它非常复杂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就像一座深不见底的冰山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你自己都不知道它的存在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200911/c465298f569c40439d82ac6c67e03ce5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200911/f01b3ca22ff547b1bb3778b5511fc123.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>催眠</strong>是年龄回溯其中一种技术</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心理医生就像愚公</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">通过催眠挖出你内心的冰山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让你可以意识到自己的潜意识</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生中每一次重大历史事件</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都会为未来埋下伏笔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就是我们常说的<strong>因果论</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200911/37a17dbd63ea4186ad78345c6f046b68.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200911/1c722fe3ce464ac69d6b47200b08dccf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的人不是觉得病根在过去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是在<strong>前世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在国外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人使用前世回溯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200911/224ae74d70bb46f180d1173bb2b24d29.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕先不谈前世是不是迷信</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先说一个<strong>病例</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美国耶鲁大学医学博士<strong>魏斯</strong>有一个病人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她总是莫名焦虑、恐惧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生活一团糟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花了18个月做传统心理治疗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是魏斯尝试用前世回溯疗法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在催眠治疗状态下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">病人回忆起<strong>81个</strong>前世记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200911/549f72bd721c4e8d97d5e6233b50b35c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你记忆的错乱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有些是你大脑自带的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有些是别人强行植入的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这些都会带来无法想象的<strong>恶果</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200911/a5ad107850e14ecfa563ed3c44c6c9f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有带来好果的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200911/84a47582b3624fd3a90720d0669cc42f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>减 肥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国<strong>威斯敏斯特大学</strong>实验表明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给你灌输对某顿饭菜的错误记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可能会长期改变你的饮食选择</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200911/2d600a84e85843e09bc9368b9d910f7c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只要不断消极暗示你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小时候你吃冰淇淋烤鸡奶茶拉过肚子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你可能开始对它<strong>避而远之</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从而达到减肥效果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200911/05dddb6c8e744fbb8ca8f5664fa985bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说了辣么多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即便千辛万苦帮你提高记忆力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至更正记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让你有机会时间逆转……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你也没有诺兰大哥的任意门啊！！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是乖乖做人吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200911/3e487888a4b64046af32030964d6cacd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
